{"tid":1438432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人真係抵撚死！","createTime":"2019-08-09T18:23:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:46:49.000Z","uid":38075,"like":60,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"2858bbe1795e4dfc6896b17e444b329c7f0251d1","tid":1438432,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:23:37.000Z","msg":"由6月到依家，二百萬人和平遊行過，勇武過，有義士犧牲過，去到最後乜都爭取唔到，點解？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為香港人真係抵撚死！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n輸打贏要，同埋乜都要快，乜都驚，驚比人周，驚自己蝕底，成日想魚與熊掌兩者兼得，一班年輕人衝出去勇武，第一時間就標籤晒勇武嘅係年輕，自己係和理非，比個理由自己唔做所謂阻人搵食嘅野，爭取到就出黎分光環，失敗就割蓆，話勇武咩唔退呀果啲。太多太多低能野，不能盡錄。<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀，遊行無人理，姐係對家唔在乎民意，你勇武無人理，姐係對家唔在乎香港亂唔亂，姐係剩返咩？錢囉！你知我知，不過大家放唔開嘛！<br />\n<br />\n岩架，唔可以要求所有人係聖人，唔可以要求所有人都有豁出去嘅心，所以香港人真係抵死，唔使五毛分化你地，自己分化緊自己都未知啦！<br />\n<br />\n想抗爭你地唔該諗清楚幾件事先<br />\n<br />\n1. 對家嘅強弱係咩<br />\n共狗由創黨到依家，最叻就係滲透同分化，人多就雜，雜則亂，容易被滲透，因為香港人過份依賴領頭者嘅資訊。只要一有人開左個頭，搵幾條友幫手推下，全部人就會跟風，再一次屌柒你地，多啲自己諗下分析下先，唔好成日想像到對手太簡單，因為人地係好認真咁對付我地。<br />\n<br />\n2. 請你地認真對待呢場運動<br />\n承上，對家係一個老奸巨滑嘅黨，本來已經屌打我地啲散兵游勇。你地要視呢場運動為戰爭，一場真係影響生死存亡嘅戰爭，而唔係上左街，打爛啲玻璃，笑下啲狗就完。一個二個掛撚住打丁，對家柒下柒下又可以講一晚，何妖叫人去自慰又可以出幾個post，麻煩你地返返去行動post，文宣post，多做事，少說廢話。<br />\n<br />\n3. 請理解，勇武同和理非嘅定義<br />\n勇武同和理非並唔係講緊人，而係講緊行動嘅性質，講緊戰爭嘅戰術，講緊達到目的嘅手段，唔好再標籤自己，兄弟爬山，各自努力，講你地就識講，但唔該記住，大家係同路人，爬緊嘅係同一個山頂，我地係要逼使個政權跪低。我地唔係要去爭你做多左我做少左果啲野，而係各施其職，互相配合，所以請自行根據自己能力同取捨去參與活動，唔好再局限自己嘅身分。<br />\n<br />\n4. 國際關注已達成，勿再過於依賴<br />\n呢件事係我地香港人嘅事，國際關注係為左用黎鉗制中共，施加壓力，令佢地嘅弱點暴露出黎。好多巴絲都分析過支爆問題，同時亦印證我一開始所講嘅錢嘅問題。人地要幫嘅已經幫左，剩低嘅就要靠我地自己。<br />\n<br />\n最後，我想講，雖然香港人係抵死，但身為抵死嘅一員，我無論如何都會抗爭到底，每一個五毛，賣港賊，仲有多不勝數嘅助紂為虐嘅人，你地會有被清算嘅一日！"},{"pid":"752ffbcf668029c2929ba1c559e3fd3e9c98396f","tid":1438432,"uid":292881,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:31:29.000Z","msg":"香港人窮得只有錢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係再唔槍口一致對準政權<br />\n以後你地就唔洗再努力搵錢<br />\n準備擁抱大灣區啦！</span><br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山！<br />\n不分化！不割席！"},{"pid":"a14a5b16893c14e9dc9ea685d2facb626991ae7e","tid":1438432,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:37:20.000Z","msg":"推到五毛狗死晒"},{"pid":"2ad0e2abb1ba1d2697e97c2859c99b63c51f5811","tid":1438432,"uid":38075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:41:20.000Z","msg":"邊推邊欣賞五毛有隊形咁開無聊post洗版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30872209e54bfd3a3a5146a9ac65839686973bbe","tid":1438432,"uid":199712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:42:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但係民意仍然要理<br />\n因為民意可以令我哋嘅行動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出師有名</span><br />\n所以要keep住做文宣<br />\n啲中立派唔會無啦啦變黄架<br />\n大家勇武嘅同時要做文宣吸引中間派過嚟<br />\n咁多位手足加油"},{"pid":"1eff7a04f21dbae24822016b0ff3b89f0c4d2989","tid":1438432,"uid":292881,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30872209e54bfd3a3a5146a9ac65839686973bbe","tid":1438432,"uid":199712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:42:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但係民意仍然要理<br />\n因為民意可以令我哋嘅行動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出師有名</span><br />\n所以要keep住做文宣<br />\n啲中立派唔會無啦啦變黄架<br />\n大家勇武嘅同時要做文宣吸引中間派過嚟<br />\n咁多位手足加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"其實要歸邊就歸左邊，<br />\n扮瞓既人係屌打佢都唔會醒。<br />\n<br />\n不過咁，<br />\n文宣係要不斷做，起勢做，擺個靚姿態；<br />\n勇武係要繼續愈戰愈勇，大大力錫春袋都okay ；<br />\n有乜做乜，<br />\n能力有幾多就做幾多，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">香港人已經無得再輸。</span>"},{"pid":"5182467aadd6ed3416df71de2c0dc5b7f3258630","tid":1438432,"uid":38075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"30872209e54bfd3a3a5146a9ac65839686973bbe","tid":1438432,"uid":199712,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:42:26.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n但係民意仍然要理<br />\n因為民意可以令我哋嘅行動<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">出師有名</span><br />\n所以要keep住做文宣<br />\n啲中立派唔會無啦啦變黄架<br />\n大家勇武嘅同時要做文宣吸引中間派過嚟<br />\n咁多位手足加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:50:30.000Z","msg":"民宣要做，因為係一種姿態，話比有心人聽我地嘅意念，該做都要做，政治本來就是一個舞台"},{"pid":"41f3077e3d8d6b927835458b0e7cf231d85c664e","tid":1438432,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:55:02.000Z","msg":"屌，個個有用既post 都沉，<br />\n啲on9 post 就起勢推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推呀！<br />\n五大訴求呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c35d4c001401066486c3356a3e5a331a6afb7cb","tid":1438432,"uid":292881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:58:51.000Z","msg":"幫推！<br />\n<br />\n真係好on9 ，<br />\n連登仔係咪死撚哂？<br />\n對準政權呀DLLM！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求！缺一不可！"},{"pid":"b701f74a7e3c34a4ecb188e9c8d3492ba9a41b6d","tid":1438432,"uid":208932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:00:41.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"be43a613a20b9633ad6556663490910bb0614288","tid":1438432,"uid":292471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:06:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ab3c7fbe1891fcf68cd2b69daf28918118e36f5","tid":1438432,"uid":274136,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:06:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><em><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不撤不散 各有各做<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span></ins></em></strong><br />\n唔好意思 阻你一陣<br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人重點日程：<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>8月9-11日</strong>：機場和你飛&bull;萬人接機&bull;一連三日(1300)</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>8月10日</strong>：銀髮族遞信「900警總」&gt;「1000律政司辦公室」&gt;「1100特首辦」<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：守護孩子未來親子遊行（1030愛丁堡廣場）<br />\n<strong>8月10日</strong>：大埔遊行（1400大埔巴士總站）（反對通知書）</span><br />\n-<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>8月11日</strong>：港島東遊行（1300維多利亞公園）<br />\n<strong>8月11日</strong>：深水埗遊行（1430楓樹街遊樂場）</span></span>"},{"pid":"0d21392d14f558804b56931ba2a437170145d01a","tid":1438432,"uid":210995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:07:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點 1. 對家嘅強弱係咩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好比人亂帶風向呀屌你地</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f674c863f53a898b819a454a0514ad28dcf13fa8","tid":1438432,"uid":153258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:12:04.000Z","msg":"抵唔抵死都好 入黎救救落單手足<br />\n<br />\n見到班防暴做埋畜蟲既野，就諗起自己<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1425253\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1425253</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc583454852e014cad881c603488a27233c715cb","tid":1438432,"uid":190291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:12:20.000Z","msg":"推啊 唔好比佢沉!!!"},{"pid":"ae0ec453c023fced6b2580aabbbe445c0401981b","tid":1438432,"uid":245968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:18:08.000Z","msg":"推啊屌！再輸就真係乜鳩都無"},{"pid":"122550f9b788ab9bd8790a30c520320fcb679371","tid":1438432,"uid":132032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:22:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11410025ba7237265de1fe4eb4f1fe7780288de3","tid":1438432,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:26:04.000Z","msg":"[心理戰] 唔好再講和理非 唔好再講勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我哋一定要贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8e03ada53667ca8f5f13b3861851e269af50ef1","tid":1438432,"uid":186782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:27:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"087e97df39e8f2e59338ba8e33e4375164cb8458","tid":1438432,"uid":184096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:28:39.000Z","msg":"咁有咩要做<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n求大家幫幫我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n［8.10大埔尋貓］走失名為豬油（or自由）嘅貓咪，希望大家一齊幫手入嚟大埔搵貓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438472</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"19e9a9ce5067f2c6f28da806eb38f604d02f91f6","tid":1438432,"uid":2883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:13:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dd3cb4359fe9c3e177dc3f16ea8d451261f0fcf3","tid":1438432,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:31:35.000Z","msg":"小心等陣班人話你分化呀<br />\n依家吹緊風要成個運動要和理非"},{"pid":"594529b80d70bc3fdd0affd52c27c3d47ebf86eb","tid":1438432,"uid":294778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:40:56.000Z","msg":"其實都預咗最終失敗，但真係唔甘心就咁放棄&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4577002917451dfb43bd5cc19d5bfe2883848e","tid":1438432,"uid":151352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:45:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee513b9ca1c0e1a074cda376e767c3c6eee451f","tid":1438432,"uid":269982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:47:31.000Z","msg":"push"}]}